{"pageDepth":2,"statusbar":"<美化><界面><启动>","beginning":"##这是提示词示例，建议放在世界书system，顺序9999-当{{user}}与其他角色发生对话时，按照以下格式生成对话，必须包含编号：\n#对话开始#\n[dh①{{发言者名字}}②{{立绘编号}}③{{内容}}]\n[dh①{{发言者名字}}②{{立绘编号}}③{{内容}}]\n#对话结束#\n-发言者名字：\n  -若该条内容为环境描写、剧情描述等无发言者内容，则发言者名字填写空格\n  -若{{user}}未得知对方姓名，则发言者名字处先填写\"???\"或身份，当得知对方姓名后再填写姓名\n-内容：\n  -按照Galgame的文本格式风格描写，每条只包括一个人的一句话，不需要加引号，正确使用句号，如果是思考内容则加括号\n  -包含{{user}}与其他交互角色的对话、{{user}}的内心思考、环境描写、动作描写、叙事描写等。\n  -每条内容不超过50字，一段长内容可拆分为多句\n-立绘编号：\n  -只有七名设定中的女角色具有立绘，{{user}}没有立绘。根据发言者及其本句发言情绪使用合适的立绘\n  -编号格式必须使用\"姓氏+情绪编号\"，如\"沈3\"表示显示沈清雨的立绘且情绪为紧张/害怕。情绪编号仅包括以下7种：\n  -中性/冷静(1)：用途：日常对话、信息说明、理性讨论。特征：眼神正常、嘴角自然、无明显情绪波动\n  -轻微正向(2)：用途：恋爱互动、队友鼓励、放松时刻、苦中作乐。特征：轻微微笑、眼神柔和\n  -紧张/害怕(3)：用途：发现异常、夜晚动静、推理关键点、危险来临。特征：眼睛微张、眉微皱、嘴轻抿\n  -严肃/决断(4)：用途：争论、战术讨论、道德抉择、领导时刻。特征：眉收紧、目光坚定、嘴线偏直\n  -愤怒/对立(5)：用途：派系冲突、被背叛、情绪爆发、争吵场景。特征：眉压低、目光锐利、嘴张或咬牙\n  -失落/恐惧(6)：用途：资源枯竭、情感崩溃、夜间恐怖。特征：眼神下垂或颤动、嘴角下压、有轻微泪光\n  -害羞/羞耻(7)：用途：暧昧、被夸奖、情感暴露、说出秘密。特征：轻微脸红、目光回避、嘴角轻抿\n-示例：[dh①沈清雨②沈2③就像这样。]","regex_scripts":[{"id":-1,"replaceString":"<style>\n.sidebar{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;position:fixed;right:0;z-index:200}\n.sidebar1{box-sizing: border-box;width:26px;background:#5a7c65;padding:8px 3px;border:2px solid #d5e8d5;border-radius:12px 0 0 12px;color:#d5e8d5;writing-mode:vertical-rl;text-orientation:mixed;font-size:12px;font-weight:bold;text-align:center;letter-spacing:1px;box-shadow:-2px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);}\n\n.gal-interface {position:fixed;width:100%;height:100%;z-index:100;bottom:0px; display:block;box-sizing: border-box;backdrop-filter: blur(5px);}\n.chatbox{display:flex}\n.namebox {position:absolute;bottom:120px;color:#3c5243;border:2px #5a7c65 solid;background:#d5e8d5;border-radius:10px;width:100px;height:40px;display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;box-sizing: border-box}\n.messagebox {position:absolute;bottom:0;border: 4px #5a7c65 solid;border-top-right-radius:30px;width:100%;height:120px;box-sizing: border-box;background:rgba(90, 124, 101, 0.7);z-index:-1;display:flex;flex-direction:row;}\n.closebox {color:#FFF;position:absolute;bottom:85px;right:15px;height:20px;width:20px;border-radius:50%;background:#3c5243; display:flex;align-items: center;justify-content: center;}\n.hidebox {color:#FFF;position:absolute;bottom:85px;right:45px;height:20px;width:20px;font-size:10px;border-radius:50%;background:#3c5243;display:flex;align-items: center;justify-content: center;}\n.autobox {color:#FFF;position:absolute;bottom:85px;left:15px;height:20px;width:20px;font-size:10px;border-radius:50%;background:#3c5243;display:flex;align-items: center;justify-content: center;}\n.turnpage{display:flex;align-items: center;justify-content: center;width:15%;color:#FFF;font-size:24px;box-sizing: border-box;}\n.message{width:70%;box-sizing: border-box;padding:15px 10px;color:#FFF;letter-spacing: 0.5px;overflow:scroll}\n.illustration-wrap{position:absolute;bottom:0;right:0;height:60vh;width:100vw;z-index:-2;pointer-events:auto;}\n.illustration {position:absolute;bottom:0;right:0;height:100%;width:auto;max-width:100%;z-index:-2;}\n.illustration-layer{display:none;opacity:0;transition:opacity .18s ease;}\n.illustration-current{z-index:-2;}\n.illustration-prev,.illustration-next{z-index:-3;}\n.mdata{display:none;}\n.pagenum{position:absolute;right:20px;bottom:10px;color:#FFF;font-size:10px;}\n\n.messagebtn{padding:5px; background:#5a7c65; color:#d5e8d5; border-radius:5px;margin:5px;}\n.messagedata{display:none;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;margin:10px 0;padding:8px;border:1px solid rgba(213,232,213,0.28);border-radius:14px;background:rgba(52,78,65,0.72);box-shadow:0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.18);box-sizing:border-box;color:#edf6ef;backdrop-filter:blur(8px);}\n.dataitem{width:100%;padding:10px 12px;box-sizing:border-box;border:1px solid rgba(213,232,213,0.18);border-radius:10px;background:rgba(90,124,101,0.28);}\n.dataitem:last-child{margin-bottom:0;}\n.dataname{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#d5e8d5;margin-bottom:4px;}\n.datacontent{padding-left:0;font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:#edf6ef;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-word;}\n\n.gal-settings{position:fixed;left:50%;top:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);z-index:10001;display:none;}\n.gal-settings-card{width:min(360px,86vw);border:2px solid #3c5243;border-radius:16px;background:rgba(52,78,65,0.96);box-shadow:0 14px 36px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);color:#edf6ef;backdrop-filter:blur(8px);padding:12px 14px;box-sizing:border-box;}\n.gal-settings-head{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:10px;margin-bottom:10px;}\n.gal-settings-title{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#e8f5ea;}\n.gal-settings-close{width:24px;height:24px;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid rgba(213,232,213,0.28);background:rgba(90,124,101,0.5);color:#d5e8d5;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;cursor:pointer;}\n.gal-settings-body{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;}\n.gal-settings-row{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px;}\n.gal-settings-label{font-size:12px;color:#d5e8d5;}\n.gal-settings-input{width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;border:1px solid rgba(213,232,213,0.3);border-radius:10px;background:rgba(90,124,101,0.35);color:#edf6ef;padding:8px 10px;font-size:12px;outline:none;}\n.gal-settings-input:focus{border-color:rgba(213,232,213,0.6);box-shadow:0 0 0 2px rgba(213,232,213,0.12);}\n</style>","scriptName":"美化","findRegex":"<美化>"},{"id":-1,"replaceString":"<div class=\"sidebar\" style=\"top:150px\" onclick=\"event.stopPropagation();\">\n<div class=\"sidebar1\" onclick=\"event.stopPropagation();var panel=document.querySelector('.gal-settings');var btn=this;var open=panel&&panel.style.display!=='none';if(panel){panel.style.display=open?'none':'block';}\">设置</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"gal-interface\" style=\"display:none;\" onclick=\"event.stopPropagation();document.querySelector('.chatbox').style.display='flex'\">\n<div class=\"chatbox\">\n<div class=\"namebox\"></div>\n<div class=\"closebox\" onclick=\"event.stopPropagation();document.querySelector('.gal-interface').style.display='none';var btn=document.querySelector('.autobox');if(window.__galAutoTimer){clearTimeout(window.__galAutoTimer);window.__galAutoTimer=null;}if(btn){btn.dataset.auto='';btn.className=btn.className.replace(/\\bon\\b/g,'').replace(/\\s+/g,' ').replace(/^\\s+|\\s+$/g,'');btn.innerText='▶';}\">×</div>\n<div class=\"hidebox\" onclick=\"event.stopPropagation();document.querySelector('.chatbox').style.display='none';\">▼</div>\n<div class=\"autobox\" onclick=\"event.stopPropagation();var btn=this;var message=document.querySelector('.message');var page=document.querySelector('.pagenum');function stop(){if(window.__galAutoTimer){clearTimeout(window.__galAutoTimer);window.__galAutoTimer=null;}btn.dataset.auto='';btn.className=btn.className.replace(/\\bon\\b/g,'').replace(/\\s+/g,' ').replace(/^\\s+|\\s+$/g,'');btn.innerText='▶';}function nextDelay(){if(!message){return 1000;}var text=message.fullText||message.textContent||'';var len=text.length||0;var typing=parseInt(window.__galTypingMs,10);var pause=parseInt(window.__galAutoPauseMs,10);if(isNaN(typing))typing=30;if(isNaN(pause))pause=1000;return pause+len*typing;}function tick(){if(!message||!page){stop();return;}var total=parseInt(page.dataset.total||'1');var current=parseInt(page.dataset.current||'0');if(current>=total){stop();return;}message.click();var delay=nextDelay();window.__galAutoTimer=setTimeout(tick,delay);}if(btn.dataset.auto==='1'){stop();return;}btn.dataset.auto='1';if(btn.className.indexOf('on')<0)btn.className+=(btn.className?' ':'')+'on';btn.innerText='⏸︎';tick();\">▶</div>\n<div class=\"messagebox\" >\n<div class=\"turnpage\" onclick=\"var message=this.nextElementSibling;if(message.animating){ clearInterval(message.timer);message.textContent = message.fullText; message.animating = false;return; } var page=document.querySelector('.pagenum'); var current=parseInt(page.dataset.current);if(current>1){current-=2;page.dataset.current=current.toString();message.click()};\">◀</div>\n<div class=\"message\" onclick=\"(function(container){ if(container.animating){ clearInterval(container.timer);container.textContent = container.fullText; container.animating = false;return; }var page=document.querySelector('.pagenum');var current=parseInt(page.dataset.current);var total=parseInt(page.dataset.total);if(current<total){var data=document.querySelector('.mdata').children[current];var fullText =data.querySelector('.datacontent').innerText;container.fullText = fullText;document.querySelector('.namebox').innerText=data.querySelector('.dataname').innerText;var imgSrc = data.dataset.img;if(window.galApp&&window.galApp.setGalIllustration){window.galApp.setGalIllustration(imgSrc);}container.textContent = '';var index = 0;var typing=parseInt(window.__galTypingMs,10);if(isNaN(typing))typing=30;if(typing<=0){container.textContent=fullText;container.animating=false;}else{container.animating = true;container.timer = setInterval(function(){ if(index < fullText.length){container.textContent += fullText[index]; index++; } else { clearInterval(container.timer); container.animating = false; }}, typing);} current++;page.dataset.current=current.toString();page.innerText=page.dataset.current+'/'+page.dataset.total;if(window.galApp&&window.galApp.preloadNextGalImage&&current<total){var nextData=document.querySelector('.mdata').children[current];window.galApp.preloadNextGalImage(nextData?nextData.dataset.img:'');}}else{document.querySelector('.gal-interface').style.display='none';}})(this)\"></div>\n<div class=\"turnpage\" onclick=\"this.previousElementSibling.click()\">▶</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mdata\"></div>\n<div class=\"pagenum\" data-current=\"0\" data-total=\"1\">0/1</div></div>\n<div class=\"illustration-wrap\" onclick=\"document.querySelector('.chatbox').style.display='flex'\">\n<img id=\"illustration_a\" class=\"illustration illustration-layer\" src=\"x\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none';\">\n<img id=\"illustration_b\" class=\"illustration illustration-layer\" src=\"x\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none';\">\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"gal-settings\" style=\"display:none;\" onclick=\"event.stopPropagation();\">\n<div class=\"gal-settings-card\" onclick=\"event.stopPropagation();\">\n<div class=\"gal-settings-head\">\n<div class=\"gal-settings-title\">对话设置</div>\n<div class=\"gal-settings-close\" onclick=\"event.stopPropagation();var panel=this.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement;panel.style.display='none';\">×</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"gal-settings-body\">\n<div class=\"gal-settings-row\">\n<div class=\"gal-settings-label\">打字速度 (ms/字)</div>\n<input class=\"gal-settings-input\" type=\"number\" min=\"0\" step=\"1\" value=\"30\" oninput=\"event.stopPropagation();var v=parseInt(this.value,10);if(isNaN(v))v=30;if(v<0)v=0;window.__galTypingMs=v;localStorage.setItem('gal_typing_ms',String(v));\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"gal-settings-row\">\n<div class=\"gal-settings-label\">自动播放停顿 (ms)</div>\n<input class=\"gal-settings-input\" type=\"number\" min=\"0\" step=\"50\" value=\"1000\" oninput=\"event.stopPropagation();var v=parseInt(this.value,10);if(isNaN(v))v=1000;if(v<0)v=0;window.__galAutoPauseMs=v;localStorage.setItem('gal_auto_pause_ms',String(v));\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n","scriptName":"gal界面","findRegex":"<界面>"},{"id":-1,"replaceString":"<img src=\"x\" style=\"display:none;\" onerror=\"(function(self){var mainTextarea=document.querySelector('.chat .chat-bottom .uni-textarea .chat-input-scope textarea');if(mainTextarea){mainTextarea.value='';mainTextarea.dispatchEvent(new Event('input'));}if(window.galReady)return;var app=window.galApp||{};var storedTyping=localStorage.getItem('gal_typing_ms');var storedPause=localStorage.getItem('gal_auto_pause_ms'); if(typeof window.__galTypingMs==='undefined'){ window.__galTypingMs=storedTyping!==null?parseInt(storedTyping,10):30; if(isNaN(window.__galTypingMs))window.__galTypingMs=30;}if(typeof window.__galAutoPauseMs==='undefined'){window.__galAutoPauseMs=storedPause!==null?parseInt(storedPause,10):1000;if(isNaN(window.__galAutoPauseMs))window.__galAutoPauseMs=1000;}var settingsPanel=document.querySelector('.gal-settings');if(settingsPanel){var inputs=settingsPanel.querySelectorAll('.gal-settings-input');for(var si=0;si<inputs.length;si++){var input=inputs[si];if(!input)continue;var parent=input.parentElement;if(!parent)continue;var label=parent.querySelector('.gal-settings-label');var labelText=label?label.textContent:'';if(labelText.indexOf('打字速度')>=0){input.value=String(window.__galTypingMs);}else if(labelText.indexOf('自动播放停顿')>=0){input.value=String(window.__galAutoPauseMs);}}}var interface=document.querySelector('.gal-interface');var cb=document.querySelector('.chat-bottom').offsetHeight;var ch=window.innerHeight-document.querySelector('.topTabbar').offsetHeight-cb;interface.style.bottom=cb+'px';interface.style.height=ch+'px';&图片&app.galImageCodes=[];app.galImageCache={};app.galPreloadStarted=false;app.galPreloadFinished=false;function getIllustrationLayer(name){return document.getElementById('illustration_'+name);}function getIllustrationLayers(){return {a:getIllustrationLayer('a'),b:getIllustrationLayer('b')};}function setLayerVisible(layer,visible){if(!layer)return;layer.style.display=visible?'block':'none';layer.style.opacity=visible?'1':'0';}function hideAllIllustrations(){var layers=getIllustrationLayers();setLayerVisible(layers.a,false);setLayerVisible(layers.b,false);}function attachLayerLoad(layer,url,mode,layerName){if(!layer)return;layer.onload=function(){layer.dataset.ready='1'; if(mode==='show'&&app.galPendingShowUrl===url){app.swapGalLayer(layerName,url);}};layer.onerror=function(){layer.dataset.ready='0';if(mode==='show'&&app.galPendingShowUrl===url){hideAllIllustrations();}};}app.buildGalImageCodes=function(){var parts=app.galNameParts||[];var acc=[''];var i;var j;var k;var group;if(!parts.length){app.galImageCodes=[];return app.galImageCodes;}for(i=0;i<parts.length;i++){group=parts[i];if(!group||!group.length){app.galImageCodes=[];return app.galImageCodes;}var next=[];for(j=0;j<acc.length;j++){for(k=0;k<group.length;k++){next.push(String(acc[j])+String(group[k]));}}acc=next;}app.galImageCodes=acc;return acc;};app.resolveGalImageUrl=function(code){code=String(code||'').replace(/^\\s+|\\s+$/g,'');if(!code||code==='x'||code==='none')return '';return app.galImageBaseUrl+code+app.galImageExt;};app.preloadGalImage=function(url){if(!url)return null;var cached=app.galImageCache[url];if(cached)return cached;cached={status:'loading',img:new Image()};app.galImageCache[url]=cached;cached.img.onload=function(){cached.status='loaded';};cached.img.onerror=function(){cached.status='error';};cached.img.src=url;return cached;};app.preloadAllGalImages=function(){var list=app.galImageCodes.length?app.galImageCodes:app.buildGalImageCodes();var total=0;var finished=0;var i;function markDone(){finished++;if(finished>=total){app.galPreloadFinished=true;}}for(i=0;i<list.length;i++){var url=app.resolveGalImageUrl(list[i]);if(!url)continue;total++;var cached=app.preloadGalImage(url);if(!cached){markDone();continue;}if(cached.status==='loaded'||cached.status==='error'){markDone();continue;}cached.img.onload=function(){cached.status='loaded';markDone();};cached.img.onerror=function(){cached.status='error';markDone();};}if(!total){app.galPreloadFinished=true;}};app.ensureGalPreload=function(){if(app.galPreloadStarted)return;app.galPreloadStarted=true;app.preloadAllGalImages();};app.swapGalLayer=function(layerName,url){var layers=getIllustrationLayers();var showLayer=layers[layerName];var hideLayer=layers[layerName==='a'?'b':'a'];if(!showLayer)return;if(url&&showLayer.dataset.url!==url)return;setLayerVisible(showLayer,true);setLayerVisible(hideLayer,false);app.galActiveLayer=layerName;app.galPendingShowUrl='';};app.preloadNextGalImage=function(imgCode){var url=app.resolveGalImageUrl(imgCode);var layers=getIllustrationLayers();var nextLayerName=app.galActiveLayer==='a'?'b':'